---
import { TextSection } from '@components/odyssey-theme';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Page.astro';
import HeroSection from '../../components/sections/heros/HeroSection.astro';

const seo = {
    title: 'About SCI-NAD',
    description: "Learn more about SCI-NAD's mission to advance the frontiers of neuroscience through deep-tech innovation.",
};
---

<Layout {seo}>
    <HeroSection>
        <div slot="text-container">
            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>
                SCI-NAD (Synaptic Computational Interface for NeuroAdvancement Design) is pioneering a new era in neurotechnology by making the complexities of the brain accessible to everyone. We are dedicated to transforming how neurotech research and education are conducted, merging advanced computational tools with an intuitive, gamified experience. Our platform empowers users—from experts to enthusiasts—to explore, simulate, and understand neural activity in an interactive 3D environment.
            </p>
        </div>
        <picture slot="image-container">
            <img
                src="/assets/images/n.jpg"
                alt="About Us"
                id="Neuron"
            />
        </picture>
    </HeroSection>

    <TextSection narrow>
        <h2>Our Vision</h2>
        <p>
            At SCI-NAD, our vision is to <strong>democratize neurotechnology</strong>. We aim to bridge the gap between intricate neurotech concepts and practical, engaging learning experiences. By providing an accessible platform for deep-tech neuroscientific exploration, we empower users with advanced tools and a collaborative community to tackle the most challenging problems in neuroscience.
        </p>
    </TextSection>

    <TextSection narrow>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            <strong>Empowering Through Innovation:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Make Neurotechnology Accessible:</strong> Simplify complex brain-electrode interactions through an intuitive 3D brain mapping tool.</li>
            <li><strong>Foster Interactive Learning:</strong> Utilize gamified learning pathways to guide users from novice to expert levels in neurotech.</li>
            <li><strong>Promote Collaborative Exploration:</strong> Offer a platform where users can share simulations, research, and insights, fostering a vibrant community of neurotech enthusiasts.</li>
            <li><strong>Advance Scientific Understanding:</strong> Provide cutting-edge visualizations and real-time simulations to deepen the understanding of neural activity.</li>
        </ul>
    </TextSection>

    <TextSection narrow>
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
            <strong>Enthusiasts!!</strong>
        </p>
    </TextSection>

    <TextSection narrow>
        <h2>The Problem We Solve</h2>
        <p>
            <strong>Making Complexity Accessible:</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            Understanding brain-electrode interactions and neural data can be daunting due to the complexity and inaccessibility of traditional tools. SCI-NAD addresses this challenge by providing:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Intuitive 3D Models:</strong> Simplifying the visualization of neural structures and electrode placements.</li>
            <li><strong>Interactive Simulations:</strong> Allowing users to see real-time neural activity and the impact of their inputs.</li>
            <li><strong>Integrated Knowledge Graphs:</strong> Linking research papers, datasets, and annotations directly to the visual models for contextual learning.</li>
        </ul>
    </TextSection>

    <TextSection narrow>
        <h2>Our Solution</h2>
        <p>
            <strong>An All-in-One Neurotech Platform:</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            Experience a seamless integration of advanced tools and user-friendly interfaces:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Drag-and-Drop Interface:</strong> Easily place electrodes and create 3D montages with a simple, intuitive system.</li>
            <li><strong>Real-Time Neural Simulations:</strong> Visualize and decode neural data instantly using state-of-the-art technologies.</li>
            <li><strong>Knowledge Integration:</strong> Access and connect to a wealth of research papers and datasets through interactive knowledge graphs.</li>
            <li><strong>Cross-Platform Accessibility:</strong> Use SCI-NAD on any device, anywhere, ensuring that learning and exploration are always within reach.</li>
        </ul>
    </TextSection>

    <TextSection narrow>
        <h2>Our Impact</h2>
        <p>
            <strong>Transforming Neurotech Engagement:</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            By simplifying complex concepts and fostering an interactive learning environment, SCI-NAD is reshaping how neurotechnology is taught and understood. Our platform:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Encourages Innovation:</strong> Empowers users to experiment and discover, leading to new insights and breakthroughs.</li>
            <li><strong>Builds Community:</strong> Creates a collaborative space where knowledge and ideas are freely shared.</li>
            <li><strong>Inspires Future Leaders:</strong> Engages and educates the next generation of neuroscientists and technologists.</li>
        </ul>
    </TextSection>
</Layout>
